snippet.title: Bat 'n Ball gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Bat 'n Ball, Dos PC game produced by ButtonSoft in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/bat-n-ball/6765/
Bat 'n Ball is a very interesting game of action in which test your dexterity and speed reflections.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
